Oppportunities with Quotes and Quote Line Items Report

View details about the quotes associated with opportunities, and the line items for each quote. The default settings provide the most commonly used information from each object, but you can customize the report to see any opportunity, quote, or quote line item field.

You can select the "converted" version of an amount or total column to show its value converted to a different currency.
The default report shows results grouped by Opportunity Name and then by Quote Name. Each quote line item is listed beneath its associated quote.
